{"tid":1384143,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［各位入一入嚟解夢］發夢見到港鐵調唔到頭","createTime":"2019-07-30T00:24:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:34:25.000Z","uid":117642,"like":109,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f3eeec58814ab8aaecac3cbf8f717fc145ff66e1","tid":1384143,"uid":117642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:24:47.000Z","msg":"發夢見到去大站搞（例如調景嶺）係唔會對列車服務有好大影響<br />\n因為隧道有好多調頭位<br />\n係可以行細圈<br />\n而且大站嘅Man Power 係超多<br />\n所以好快會有人Support<br />\n如果真係搞，可以去啲細站<br />\n港島線：灣仔至炮台山<br />\n將軍澳線：將軍澳<br />\n荃灣線：佐敦，深水埗至美孚<br />\n觀塘線：石硤尾至黃大仙<br />\n搞以上路段，車就無得行細圈，即係車一定會塞"},{"pid":"b4f5de6920c4cfc3f5630132ad49a4a4f1bcde34","tid":1384143,"uid":117642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:30:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ce8c5740af93c658e5b0b76fb027b7f1697ed37","tid":1384143,"uid":290027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b88b9d176592c833bec7bf30994128270cffa20","tid":1384143,"uid":117642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ce8c5740af93c658e5b0b76fb027b7f1697ed37","tid":1384143,"uid":290027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"無人理好灰。。。"},{"pid":"75413a3fa80a74eec87a269de23c0e2aa371dd98","tid":1384143,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:43:52.000Z","msg":"叉錯腳 跌電話 暈左 架車死火之類好常見<br />\n<br />\n個人無事要繼續行程<br />\n<br />\n唔好阻人 唔要入黑房抄牌<br />\n<br />\n一齊體現香港人合作精神! 無人不合作 只有超合作"},{"pid":"626a462ec24e12f48c9f7f31173fe2c2711b3a69","tid":1384143,"uid":108584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T00:43:53.000Z","msg":"轉車站塞都冇用？呢啲站會唔會有機會列車可以飛站？"},{"pid":"a8a28a4d4c82acb56a0f21a788a51df987a0fdb0","tid":1384143,"uid":117642,"like":10,"dislike":0,